&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Beautiful is better than ugly.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simple is better than complex.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complex is better than complicated.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Readability counts.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;There should be one–and preferably only one–obvious way to do it.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Now is better than never.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
